{"tid":1309676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召集一眾被迫睇TVB嘅巴絲「恥與為伍！」，內有TVB廣告客戶名單 + FB link","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:09:30.000Z","uid":267969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10ac376e4cbb101e4e0328ab4f9a8d8a8d936d5e","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"首先，TVB雖然唔係主線，但仍然係大boss前嘅攔路虎，如果唔明點解要打TVB嘅話，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家入嚟欣賞下TVB新聞點幫大家扣血</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>警方旺角清場行動-有團體到警總報案促徹查議員阻差辦公<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhjNxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhjNxS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家我同team member# 每日都捱更抵夜update <strong>TVB廣告客戶名單</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實在冇多餘時間再睇TVB mark 廣告，所以懇請被迫睇TVB 嘅你出手相助，最基本係mark 8:00-9:00pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間就mark埋9:00-10:30pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1. 為免大家重覆effort，請喺每日6:00pm 前，喺呢個post 舉手做「恥與為伍！」<br />\n2. 開post format，請參考<br />\n<blockquote>今天81台黃金時段一共有七個廣告達20秒，恥與為伍 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/QRtRpU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/QRtRpU</a></blockquote><br />\n3. 記得開post，標題要加日期 (2019-07-12)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵制TVB 行動越見成效，好多廣告客戶都淆底，但我哋一定要最少<strong>堅持去FB 留言+罷買到10月</strong>，因為根據消息，TVB就會喺10月同廣告客戶傾下年嘅Commitment<br />\n當然，呢個係香港人嘅長期抗爭，10月只係一個短期目標<br />\n<br />\n以下就係我所講嘅名單<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TVB 廣告客戶名單 (內有FB link + 留言template)</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong>請廣傳</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit#gid=1387523971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA%2Fedit%23gid%3D1387523971&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUylDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=f8687ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit#gid=1387523971</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>被迫睇TVB唔緊要<br />\n只要每星期或每月付出１小時 mark廣告，一樣可以抗爭！<br />\n大家一齊，恥與為伍！</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">#Team member 包括開展一至三波嘅巴絲打匕戈尕孓、HKismyhome，家樂牌通心粉 etc.</span>"},{"pid":"9be93eb00848930681c98ee1fc4aaa974280e66b","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407827bc3bb5855f3bbf31b954ccfe942a1edee2","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"今日有冇人做<br />\n要打贏TVB，需要付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd2585c08e8c66544a298732bb2dfb7d279270","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37d6abe8d6bc195bf7b784a9a7c62448e4d4aea","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24ebb7db06d7776144b5a92dbd47a16cfa3bff9","tid":1309676,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.g